==English==
===Alternative spellings===
* [[apres]], [[aprés]] ''(nonstandard)''

===Etymology===
French '''[[#French|après]]'''.

===Preposition===
'''après'''
# After. 
 
===Usage note===
Often hyphenated to its referent, following conventions of English multi-word&ndash;modifier hyphenation.
 
